  <entry>
    <title>120-Minute Session on Robotic Colorectal Cancer Surgery with Semi-Live Surgery</title>
    <link rel="alternate" href="https://www.apcir.pt/120-minute-session-on-robotic-colorectal-cancer-surgery" />
    <link rel="enclosure" type="image/png" href="https://irp.cdn-website.com/443a37e1/dms3rep/multi/3-120-Minute-Session-on-Robotic-Colorectal-Cancer-Surgery-1a.png" length="669718" />
    <author>
      <name />
    </author>
    <updated>2025-02-05T15:32:09Z</updated>
    <published>2025-02-05T15:32:09Z</published>
    <content>&lt;div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;img src="https://irp.cdn-website.com/443a37e1/dms3rep/multi/3-120-Minute+Session+on+Robotic+Colorectal+Cancer+Surgery.png"/&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;strong&gt;&#xD;
      
           I Portuguese Conference on Robotic Surgery
          &#xD;
    &lt;/strong&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;strong&gt;&#xD;
      
           04 e 05 Jul 2025
          &#xD;
    &lt;/strong&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span&gt;&#xD;
      
           Conference Centre Pestana Palace, Lisboa
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span&gt;&#xD;
      
           Join us for a unparalleled session dedicated to robotic surgery in colorectal cancer, with a focus on rectal cancer and right-sided colon cancer. Organized by the Portuguese Association for Robotic Surgery (APCiR), this 120-minute session will showcase some of the world’s most esteemed colorectal surgeons.
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span&gt;&#xD;
      
           The program will emphasize two critical aspects of robotic colorectal surgery: achieving proper oncologic dissection and ensuring safe anastomosis creation using the robotic platform. Attendees will gain invaluable insights through:
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;strong&gt;&#xD;
      
           Theoretical Lectures
          &#xD;
    &lt;/strong&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span&gt;&#xD;
      
           World-leading experts will share the latest advancements and best practices in robotic oncologic surgery.
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;strong&gt;&#xD;
      
           Tips &amp;amp; Tricks
          &#xD;
    &lt;/strong&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span&gt;&#xD;
      
           Practical guidance to refine surgical techniques for optimal outcomes.
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;strong&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;span&gt;&#xD;
        
            ﻿
           &#xD;
      &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
      
           Semi-Live Surgery
          &#xD;
    &lt;/strong&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span&gt;&#xD;
      
           A unique opportunity to analyze and discuss surgical procedures in detail, focusing on precision and safety.
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span&gt;&#xD;
      
           This comprehensive session is designed to provide surgeons with cutting-edge knowledge and the skills needed to deliver the highest standards of care in robotic colorectal cancer surgery. Don’t miss this essential event!
          &#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;p&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;span&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;</content>
